object.description: Luxury await you in the heart of nature and with only 54 minutes from Istanbul. (Zeray Country Bahçecik) Enjoy living the four seasons in a project that opens the doors of luxury and distinction . Mansions with an area of 964 square meters, 8 rooms and a hall overlooking the sea and located within the picturesque nature in a privileged location in Kocaeli province. The project contains all the sophistication and luxury in Mansions containing a spacious garden starting from 761(1107309$) and ending with 996(1255912$) square meters, swimming pool, sauna room, gym, Turkish bath, laundry room, room for hobbies, maid’s room, 5 master bedrooms, a gallery area for displaying photos after the Main entrance , 6 balconies, closed parking and many amenities will be nests for twelve distinguished families.

At Zeray Effect Kartepe, which consists of 130 residences, 35 commercial units, and 4 blocks as A, B1, B2, C, it is possible for you to find each type of living space you wish with following square meters: 83 m2 - 165 m2 in 1+1, 109 m2 - 199 m2 in 2+1, 135 m2 - 293 m2 in 3+1 and 185 m2 - 233 m2 in 4+1.
In Zeray Effect Kartepe, you will enjoy the luxury and comfort with the features of the project such as central floor heating system, rock wool sound insulation between double bricks, indoor/outdoor pool, snack bar, pond, fitness area, Turkish bath, sauna, activity areas, children’s playground, etc. In the project, which is planned so that at least 1 parking lot will be allocated for each flat, there will also be open or closed parking areas for guest vehicles.

Rural Sapanca, located in a position overlooking Sapanca Lake, one of the most special nature parks of our country, has been designed as 26 independent and comfortable villas on a total area of 16,500 m2 among greenery.
Villas in rural Sapanca, each with its own large landscape area and parking lot, are designed in duplex structure on 295 m2. With its outdoor swimming pool, poolside cafe and social areas where you can spend pleasant time with your loved ones, the project has been developed for you to live a happy life with your whole family.

The luxury 850 sqm mansion with panoramic sea views is located on high ground on the Azur Bank in Rockbrün Cap Maarten, France. In the elite residence with beautiful interiors 8 bedrooms, 7 bathrooms, fully equipped kitchen, dining room, 4 living rooms, sunny terrace. There is also a garage, a flowering garden and a large pool overlooking the sea. Villa is located in a quiet area in a prestigious resort. All the infrastructure nearby.

Family, life, comfort focused project Meva Anadolu consists of 750 residences in 10 blocks. Meva Anadolu, where horizontal architecture is preferred, is established on a very large area that offers spacious living opportunities. The vast majority of Meva Anadolu’s large settlement area exceeding 35 thousand m2 consists of a special landscape area.
Considering different tastes and needs, alternative options from 1+1 to 4+1, from garden duplex to terrace duplex are presented in the project. In the social facilities areas of Meva Anadolu, there are 2 outdoor swimming pools and sun terraces of 1.500 m2, 700 m2 outdoor terrace café, 750 m2 indoor sports center, 450 m2 indoor swimming pool and 750 m2 nursery as well as a 650 m2 lake, a terrace, an outdoor café, a patisserie, a waterfall, a gazebo in the middle of this lake, and a 500 m2 amphitheater for all kinds of social events and shows.

Our project consists of 9 blocks and 288 flats. There are 2 outdoor swimming pools, sunbathing terraces, basketball, volleyball, tennis courts, children's playground, walking areas and lodges in the open area where we can provide session in the site. Our indoor social facility area includes an indoor swimming pool, Turkish bath, sauna, fitness and hobby rooms. Our flat type options are garden duplex, middle floor, terrace duplex, and we have stocks ranging from 1+1 to 4+1.

BANU HOUSES Ispartakule 4, which stands out for its stylish architecture, invites you to meet in the center of life. with a land area of 4.700 m2 and a construction area of 15 thousand m2, BANU HOUSES Ispartakule 4 is located in one of the most important areas of Istanbul with its comfortable, stylish and plus-value facilities. BANU HOUSES Ispartakule 4, which consists of one single block, stands out as a family project, has only 2 + 1 and 3 + 1 apartment types, 70 apartments with lake and nature views; and it is also located in close proximity to many schools, hospitals, shopping malls and life centers in the region. BANU HOUSES Ispartakule 4 with its features and special architecture that includes every detail about life such as Turkish bath, sauna, masjid, market with world brand products located inside, indoor and outdoor parking will change your view of Istanbul with its location closed to 3rd airport, TEM and the Northern Marmara Highway

Mina Towers is located on Kadikoy one of the most ancient residential neighborhood on the Asian Side. Over looks on the Marmara Sea, this is giving it a charming view. Kadikoy area is one of the best and the most beautiful places in Istanbul because it is located in the center and still it has a large number of green areas, gardens and parks. Kadikoy is considered home for more than half a million people, especially Turkish people. What makes it a special place to everyone is the combination between modernity and history.
